WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:05.220
Hey, good morning, family. I have another

00:00:02.879 --> 00:00:05.880
video I'm going to do for you here.

00:00:05.880 --> 00:00:11.820
A lot of people are wanting to know, "Hey,

00:00:08.580 --> 00:00:14.460
how do you hear God the way you do?"and

00:00:11.820 --> 00:00:15.839
they want to know how I've had

00:00:14.460 --> 00:00:17.760
the visitations. They want to understand

00:00:15.839 --> 00:00:19.440
more about me and everything. I'm going

00:00:17.760 --> 00:00:21.840
to tell you this right now:

00:00:19.440 --> 00:00:25.019
I am nothing special.

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:27.060
Why the Lord has chosen to

00:00:25.019 --> 00:00:29.459
do what He's done in my life, I have no

00:00:27.060 --> 00:00:32.278
idea. I haven't done any kind of

00:00:29.460 --> 00:00:34.140
real supernatural prayer

00:00:32.279 --> 00:00:36.540
compared to anybody else. I've

00:00:34.140 --> 00:00:38.460
been obedient, I can tell you that. When

00:00:36.540 --> 00:00:41.879
He tells me to do something, I'm quick to

00:00:38.460 --> 00:00:43.920
obey, or I try to at least. Like for

00:00:41.879 --> 00:00:45.540
the last video, I told you about being

00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:47.460
hesitant of coming on here and telling

00:00:45.540 --> 00:00:50.100
you things on YouTube because I had a

00:00:47.460 --> 00:00:51.480
gaping wound and I didn't want to

00:00:50.100 --> 00:00:53.640
come and expose that to

00:00:51.480 --> 00:00:56.519
everybody. I've been a very

00:00:53.640 --> 00:00:57.300
private person. I'm very reclusive. I

00:00:57.300 --> 00:01:03.358
have a lot of friends, but I do

00:00:59.879 --> 00:01:05.399
not try to be real social, even with my

00:01:03.359 --> 00:01:07.020
family. Even my family thinks I'm kind of

00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:09.420
strange, as far as my mom, my

00:01:07.020 --> 00:01:10.140
dad, and my brothers and sisters.

00:01:09.420 --> 00:01:11.939
I've

00:01:10.140 --> 00:01:13.860
just been really different.

00:01:11.939 --> 00:01:17.820
That's the way I've been a lot in my

00:01:13.860 --> 00:01:19.920
life. I pray a lot. I have

00:01:17.820 --> 00:01:21.658
a very unique relationship with the Lord

00:01:19.920 --> 00:01:24.720
as far as the way I look at Him and the

00:01:21.659 --> 00:01:27.180
way I talk. I'll say

00:01:24.720 --> 00:01:28.798
that much. It all started when I was

00:01:27.180 --> 00:01:31.979
a little boy. I

00:01:28.799 --> 00:01:36.240
had bad learning disabilities

00:01:31.979 --> 00:01:38.280
all through school. I couldn't read, I

00:01:36.240 --> 00:01:41.298
couldn't write very well, I couldn't

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:45.299
spell, and I couldn't do math. I went through

00:01:41.299 --> 00:01:46.920
school in special ed programs my

00:01:45.299 --> 00:01:49.320
whole entire life.

00:01:46.920 --> 00:01:51.540
People made fun of me a lot. I got

00:01:49.320 --> 00:01:54.960
bullied every day at school, spit on,

00:01:51.540 --> 00:01:56.579
pushed down, picked on all day long. I

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:58.460
would come home and cry myself to sleep

00:01:56.579 --> 00:02:01.979
because of being bullied all the time.

00:01:58.460 --> 00:02:04.500
And so, I got up into my high school

00:02:01.979 --> 00:02:06.780
years. I still couldn't read very well, I

00:02:04.500 --> 00:02:09.598
still couldn't write very well, and I

00:02:06.780 --> 00:02:12.720
couldn't do math. So the principal came

00:02:09.598 --> 00:02:16.799
to my mom and said,

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:21.599
"Some kids are just probably going to

00:02:16.800 --> 00:02:24.000
be like bricklayers. Your

00:02:21.599 --> 00:02:27.060
son really has a hard time. He's making

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:30.780
zeros in school, he's not able to keep up,

00:02:27.060 --> 00:02:34.140
and so I would try to encourage you

00:02:30.780 --> 00:02:35.220
to just pull him out of school and let

00:02:34.140 --> 00:02:37.980
him

00:02:35.220 --> 00:02:40.020
get a trade. Let him go ahead and just

00:02:37.980 --> 00:02:42.599
work with his hands and go on

00:02:40.020 --> 00:02:45.900
with his life. He's not passing any

00:02:42.599 --> 00:02:48.060
classes; he's flunking out.

00:02:45.900 --> 00:02:50.220
I hate to say

00:02:48.060 --> 00:02:51.780
this, but I would just encourage you to

00:02:50.220 --> 00:02:54.780
go ahead and let him get a

00:02:51.780 --> 00:02:57.900
full-time job and go on with his life."So

00:02:54.780 --> 00:03:00.480
I dropped out of school and started

00:02:57.900 --> 00:03:01.739
sacking groceries. I sacked groceries for

00:03:00.480 --> 00:03:04.440
three years.

00:03:01.739 --> 00:03:06.420
Prophecy after prophecy

00:03:04.440 --> 00:03:08.700
was spoken over my life that God had a

00:03:06.420 --> 00:03:10.500
call on me to do something big. I didn't

00:03:08.700 --> 00:03:12.299
know how to implement it. My mom and dad

00:03:10.500 --> 00:03:15.120
were going to Bible school at the time,

00:03:12.300 --> 00:03:18.000
and I

00:03:15.120 --> 00:03:20.459
was trying to get my GED. I thought, "Well,

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:22.379
maybe I can get my GED."I couldn't get my GED. I

00:03:20.459 --> 00:03:24.300
went and tried to take the test and

00:03:22.379 --> 00:03:26.959
I failed.

00:03:24.300 --> 00:03:30.420
So I gave up and just started working,

00:03:26.959 --> 00:03:32.879
and worked really hard. I started

00:03:30.420 --> 00:03:35.339
learning. I started listening to tapes

00:03:32.879 --> 00:03:38.659
from ministries. I got a tape player. I

00:03:35.340 --> 00:03:41.040
listened to ministries all day long,

00:03:38.659 --> 00:03:42.899
feeding on

00:03:41.040 --> 00:03:44.940
the Word of God, listening to Kenneth

00:03:42.900 --> 00:03:46.920
Hagin. And I know some people don't like

00:03:44.940 --> 00:03:48.900
Kenneth Hagin. I don't care what you

00:03:46.920 --> 00:03:51.780
think. Let me tell you that right there; I'm going to be

00:03:48.900 --> 00:03:53.400
bold with you. I do

00:03:51.780 --> 00:03:55.739
not care what you think about Kenneth

00:03:53.400 --> 00:03:58.620
Hagin. He changed my life. He taught me

00:03:55.739 --> 00:04:00.720
everything I know. So keep your comments

00:03:58.620 --> 00:04:03.239
to yourself in the comment section. If

00:04:00.720 --> 00:04:05.159
you do rude things and talk

00:04:03.239 --> 00:04:07.200
trash about him, I'll ban you immediately.

00:04:05.159 --> 00:04:10.200
There's no tolerance for it.

00:04:07.200 --> 00:04:14.399
So I listened to him over and over

00:04:10.200 --> 00:04:15.899
again.

00:04:14.400 --> 00:04:17.820
I

00:04:15.900 --> 00:04:19.620
found these ministries, I started

00:04:17.820 --> 00:04:22.680
listening to the Word, and I fed on the Word.

00:04:22.680 --> 00:04:27.600
The Lord started

00:04:25.620 --> 00:04:29.880
imparting to me. I started fasting. The Lord said,

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:31.259
"I want you to start fasting every other

00:04:29.880 --> 00:04:33.840
day of your life."So

00:04:31.259 --> 00:04:36.060
I did this as a teenager. I started

00:04:33.840 --> 00:04:39.659
fasting every other day of my life. I did

00:04:36.060 --> 00:04:43.139
this for years. I prayed, I fasted.

00:04:39.660 --> 00:04:45.720
I would start fasting

00:04:43.139 --> 00:04:47.580
when the sun came up, all the way to when the

00:04:45.720 --> 00:04:50.160
sun came down. Then I ate dinner, and that's

00:04:47.580 --> 00:04:54.180
what I did as a young man. I kid you not, I would spend

00:04:50.160 --> 00:04:57.060
time

00:04:54.180 --> 00:04:58.560
praying in the Spirit,

00:04:58.560 --> 00:05:04.080
reading my Bible, and listening to

00:05:01.020 --> 00:05:05.820
sermons. Then I got a job; I was

00:05:04.080 --> 00:05:07.440
offered a job. I had made some friends, and

00:05:05.820 --> 00:05:09.479
they said, "We want you to come and work

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:12.479
in the ministry for us."I

00:05:09.479 --> 00:05:15.840
thought, "Wow, here's my opportunity to preach,"because

00:05:12.479 --> 00:05:18.419
I was 18 years old

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:21.239
and I was excited. I got my first job; God

00:05:18.419 --> 00:05:23.698
opened the door for me. So I started

00:05:21.240 --> 00:05:25.380
cleaning bathrooms.

00:05:23.699 --> 00:05:26.880
The Lord said, "I want you to do that."So

00:05:25.380 --> 00:05:28.979
I started cleaning for a mega

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:31.139
minister's house. I started taking care of

00:05:28.979 --> 00:05:32.940
stuff for them, cleaning their

00:05:31.139 --> 00:05:35.220
cars, and doing this. I started

00:05:32.940 --> 00:05:36.960
learning and listening to him preach. I followed

00:05:35.220 --> 00:05:39.840
ministries,

00:05:36.960 --> 00:05:41.460
doing it over and over,

00:05:39.840 --> 00:05:43.219
just praying in the Spirit and

00:05:41.460 --> 00:05:46.080
learning.

00:05:43.220 --> 00:05:47.220
So the Lord spoke to us to move to where

00:05:46.080 --> 00:05:49.560
we are now,

00:05:47.220 --> 00:05:52.500
and I thought, "Man, this is my opportunity."I

00:05:49.560 --> 00:05:54.660
was 20 or 21 years old.

00:05:52.500 --> 00:05:57.000
I had just got married. I

00:05:54.660 --> 00:05:59.100
had a prophecy over my

00:05:57.000 --> 00:06:00.180
life: "You're going to find your wife, and you're

00:05:59.100 --> 00:06:02.039
going to get married

00:06:00.180 --> 00:06:05.759
in a short amount of time."So

00:06:02.039 --> 00:06:08.219
we got married.

00:06:05.759 --> 00:06:09.900
I thought, "Man, what's

00:06:08.220 --> 00:06:12.539
going to happen? We're going to move."My

00:06:09.900 --> 00:06:14.638
mom and my dad moved to where they

00:06:12.539 --> 00:06:17.039
are, and they started a Boys Ranch. They

00:06:14.639 --> 00:06:19.320
started helping out with fatherless

00:06:17.039 --> 00:06:21.599
children.

00:06:19.320 --> 00:06:23.819
We started volunteering and

00:06:21.600 --> 00:06:26.759
helping out there,

00:06:23.819 --> 00:06:29.759
trying to help these

00:06:26.759 --> 00:06:32.039
troubled young teenagers. So we did that

00:06:29.759 --> 00:06:33.780
for about a year or two, and

00:06:32.039 --> 00:06:37.440
the Lord put us at a church. We started

00:06:33.780 --> 00:06:39.419
doing ministry at the church. I

00:06:37.440 --> 00:06:41.900
was cleaning there, and I thought, "Man, I'm going to

00:06:39.419 --> 00:06:44.580
have the opportunity to preach now."Lo

00:06:41.900 --> 00:06:46.799
and behold, the pastor didn't like me

00:06:44.580 --> 00:06:49.620
that much because I preached too

00:06:46.800 --> 00:06:51.900
charismatic for him. So he said, "No, you

00:06:49.620 --> 00:06:54.180
can clean. You'll probably never preach here."I

00:06:51.900 --> 00:06:55.500
thought, "Well, you're

00:06:54.180 --> 00:06:57.300
going to change your mind. I'm going to

00:06:55.500 --> 00:06:59.759
pray and fast, and God's going to change

00:06:57.300 --> 00:07:01.500
your mind."So the Lord said, "Brandon, I

00:06:59.759 --> 00:07:04.500
want you just to be an armor bearer. You

00:07:01.500 --> 00:07:06.600
pray for the pastor here, and I

00:07:04.500 --> 00:07:09.360
want you just to keep being here and

00:07:06.600 --> 00:07:12.360
praying."So

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:14.039
I just kept cleaning. I cleaned 90 toilets

00:07:12.360 --> 00:07:16.380
three times a week.

00:07:14.039 --> 00:07:18.960
Every single time I was in there cleaning,

00:07:16.380 --> 00:07:20.819
griping in my heart, "God, You called me to

00:07:18.960 --> 00:07:22.440
the ministry. How am I going to do

00:07:20.819 --> 00:07:24.000
anything if I'm in here cleaning these

00:07:22.440 --> 00:07:25.020
toilets? What are You going to do with my

00:07:24.000 --> 00:07:27.599
life? Are You going to do anything

00:07:25.020 --> 00:07:28.740
with me?"So I just kept cleaning the

00:07:27.599 --> 00:07:30.120
bathrooms, cleaning

00:07:28.740 --> 00:07:32.520
all the floors, doing everything.

00:07:30.120 --> 00:07:35.759
And I'd go in there and ask, "Hey, will you let me

00:07:32.520 --> 00:07:38.280
preach or do anything?""No,

00:07:35.759 --> 00:07:40.199
Brandon, you are a janitor.

00:07:38.280 --> 00:07:42.119
That's what you're going to do. You're

00:07:40.199 --> 00:07:44.460
not called to preach. We don't feel that

00:07:42.120 --> 00:07:46.979
about you. You clean."I'd say,

00:07:44.460 --> 00:07:49.919
"But I know God's called me to preach."They'd

00:07:46.979 --> 00:07:52.800
say, "No, that's not what we feel."So I kept

00:07:49.919 --> 00:07:55.740
cleaning. The

00:07:52.800 --> 00:07:57.900
Lord gave me a word. I heard a word: "Hey, I

00:07:55.740 --> 00:07:59.940
want you to go warn the pastor that judgment is

00:07:57.900 --> 00:08:02.219
coming on him. You go tell him

00:07:59.940 --> 00:08:03.960
what I'm telling you."I said, "They're going to

00:08:02.220 --> 00:08:05.460
fire me, Lord. I can't go in there

00:08:03.960 --> 00:08:07.560
and tell him that. He acts like

00:08:05.460 --> 00:08:09.299
he doesn't like me that much anyway.""Are

00:08:07.560 --> 00:08:11.819
you going to be obedient to me? Are

00:08:09.300 --> 00:08:15.599
you going to

00:08:11.819 --> 00:08:17.099
be fearful of man?"I said, "Oh, man. Okay."So I was

00:08:15.599 --> 00:08:18.599
standing in the back of the hall by

00:08:17.099 --> 00:08:21.120
his office on a Sunday night after

00:08:18.599 --> 00:08:22.440
church. Lightning was striking, and you could

00:08:21.120 --> 00:08:25.319
hear the storm blowing over. There was an

00:08:22.440 --> 00:08:29.340
actual storm happening. So I knocked on his

00:08:25.319 --> 00:08:31.319
door. He said, "Come in, what can I help you with?"I

00:08:29.340 --> 00:08:34.079
said, "The Lord has a word for you."So

00:08:31.319 --> 00:08:36.180
I gave him this word. I thought I had

00:08:34.080 --> 00:08:37.740
hit him, like just

00:08:36.179 --> 00:08:40.199
punching him. That's how strong

00:08:37.740 --> 00:08:43.020
the word was that the Lord had for me to

00:08:40.200 --> 00:08:44.640
give to him. I thought he was going to fire me

00:08:43.020 --> 00:08:46.680
right then.

00:08:44.640 --> 00:08:48.180
He didn't fire me. I think he was shocked

00:08:46.680 --> 00:08:50.219
because I came in there with such

00:08:48.180 --> 00:08:52.199
boldness, being just the cleaner.

00:08:52.200 --> 00:08:57.420
That's how it started.

00:08:54.120 --> 00:08:59.279
I started obeying Him on hard words. I

00:08:57.420 --> 00:09:01.260
started obeying Him whenever He told me

00:08:59.279 --> 00:09:03.600
to do something really hard, and then He

00:09:01.260 --> 00:09:06.120
started giving me more to do. He'd say, "Do this,"while

00:09:03.600 --> 00:09:08.040
I'd be praying. He said,

00:09:06.120 --> 00:09:10.980
"I want you to go across town and give

00:09:08.040 --> 00:09:14.040
that pastor a word. There are

00:09:10.980 --> 00:09:15.720
three witches

00:09:14.040 --> 00:09:17.339
that are after his life, trying to kill

00:09:15.720 --> 00:09:19.380
him right now, and he's in the hospital

00:09:17.339 --> 00:09:22.200
fighting for his life. I want you to

00:09:19.380 --> 00:09:24.420
go and give him a word."I said, "Are you

00:09:22.200 --> 00:09:25.920
serious? Lord, they don't know me!

00:09:24.420 --> 00:09:28.920
Are you going to do it or not?"So

00:09:25.920 --> 00:09:31.260
I said, "Yeah, sure, I'll

00:09:28.920 --> 00:09:33.000
do it."So I took my little baby at

00:09:31.260 --> 00:09:34.620
the time, put the baby on my hip, and

00:09:33.000 --> 00:09:36.600
walked in through the doors. I said, "I

00:09:34.620 --> 00:09:39.480
have a word for

00:09:36.600 --> 00:09:40.860
your pastor."The lady said, "I'm the

00:09:39.480 --> 00:09:44.220
secretary.

00:09:40.860 --> 00:09:47.220
What is the word?"I said, "Well, your pastor

00:09:44.220 --> 00:09:50.339
is sick and he's dying because of these

00:09:47.220 --> 00:09:52.019
witches casting spells on him, and I come

00:09:50.339 --> 00:09:53.220
to tell you Jesus is going to heal him

00:09:52.019 --> 00:09:55.620
and bring healing to

00:09:53.220 --> 00:09:57.720
this community."She said,

00:09:55.620 --> 00:09:59.580
"You're right. Our pastor is

00:09:57.720 --> 00:10:01.019
really sick right now,

00:09:59.580 --> 00:10:02.820
and the doctors don't know

00:10:01.019 --> 00:10:05.040
what's wrong with him."So

00:10:02.820 --> 00:10:06.720
I gave them the word. Well,

00:10:05.040 --> 00:10:09.060
that pastor started raising up; his

00:10:06.720 --> 00:10:10.860
church exploded. Then it fell

00:10:09.060 --> 00:10:13.560
because he committed adultery on his

00:10:10.860 --> 00:10:15.600
wife. Just things like that. So I have

00:10:13.560 --> 00:10:19.079
these words, and I give them when

00:10:15.600 --> 00:10:21.120
the Lord wants me to.

00:10:19.080 --> 00:10:23.040
I've just been

00:10:21.120 --> 00:10:24.540
obedient. It happens all the

00:10:23.040 --> 00:10:26.699
time. "I want you to pray for this person.

00:10:24.540 --> 00:10:29.099
Go and do this."So I developed a

00:10:26.700 --> 00:10:30.540
relationship with Him. I kept

00:10:29.100 --> 00:10:32.760
working at it. Then He said, "Keep

00:10:30.540 --> 00:10:35.399
praying and cleaning these toilets."Like

00:10:32.760 --> 00:10:37.380
I said, 90 toilets three times a

00:10:35.399 --> 00:10:39.839
week. This was a megachurch, a huge church

00:10:37.380 --> 00:10:41.700
where I worked. So I cleaned them. I'd go

00:10:39.839 --> 00:10:43.140
in there and clean them all by myself on a

00:10:41.700 --> 00:10:44.880
Saturday morning. I'd clean them all by

00:10:43.140 --> 00:10:46.800
myself on a Sunday night, clean them all

00:10:44.880 --> 00:10:47.519
by myself on Wednesdays a lot of

00:10:46.800 --> 00:10:49.140
times, cleaning

00:10:47.519 --> 00:10:51.380
the floors, waxing the floors, buffing the floors, keeping

00:10:49.140 --> 00:10:53.640
doing it.

00:10:51.380 --> 00:10:54.959
I said, "Lord, I'm doing what You've asked

00:10:53.640 --> 00:10:57.779
me to do."But He said, "Well, you're not

00:10:54.959 --> 00:10:59.160
doing it in obedience. The willing and

00:10:57.779 --> 00:11:01.439
obedient will eat the good of the land.

00:10:59.160 --> 00:11:03.480
You've

00:11:01.440 --> 00:11:05.519
been obedient, but you're not willing to

00:11:03.480 --> 00:11:07.380
do it. You're complaining in your heart

00:11:05.519 --> 00:11:09.959
towards Me."I said, "When are You going to

00:11:07.380 --> 00:11:12.779
release me from this?"He said, "When you

00:11:09.959 --> 00:11:16.640
can do it with full joy unto Me, I'll

00:11:12.779 --> 00:11:20.160
release you from this. Do it unto Me."I

00:11:16.640 --> 00:11:22.439
said, "I can't do it, Lord. I keep

00:11:20.160 --> 00:11:24.180
doing this; this is terrible. I don't want

00:11:22.440 --> 00:11:26.459
to clean these toilets anymore. I do not

00:11:24.180 --> 00:11:29.939
want to wax these floors

00:11:26.459 --> 00:11:33.839
year after year after year."Finally, as

00:11:29.940 --> 00:11:36.420
I told you about my little girl in the previous video,

00:11:33.839 --> 00:11:38.300
we had our little girl, and it took me even

00:11:36.420 --> 00:11:41.640
further down to the bottom of the ocean.

00:11:38.300 --> 00:11:43.859
With all that

00:11:41.640 --> 00:11:45.720
happening, all

00:11:45.720 --> 00:11:49.680
that's going on, I'm cleaning the

00:11:47.220 --> 00:11:51.899
bathrooms, I'm submitting to the pastor, and

00:11:49.680 --> 00:11:53.699
I'm praying for him even if I don't

00:11:51.899 --> 00:11:56.040
agree with what he's preaching. The Lord

00:11:53.700 --> 00:11:58.320
said, "Honor him. Do not touch him with

00:11:56.040 --> 00:12:01.019
your words. Pray for him, honor him,

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:03.300
and respect him, even if you don't

00:12:01.019 --> 00:12:05.279
agree. But you have to not only do it

00:12:03.300 --> 00:12:06.500
with words; you have to do it with your

00:12:05.279 --> 00:12:10.140
heart.""Are

00:12:06.500 --> 00:12:11.339
You kidding me?"I said, "Lord, this

00:12:10.140 --> 00:12:12.839
is the hardest thing I've ever been

00:12:11.339 --> 00:12:14.459
through in my life. You want me to do

00:12:12.839 --> 00:12:16.140
this? With my little girl, everything's

00:12:14.459 --> 00:12:18.479
falling apart. Now You want me to honor

00:12:16.140 --> 00:12:20.699
this man with my words

00:12:18.480 --> 00:12:23.100
and my heart, not complaining about

00:12:20.700 --> 00:12:24.899
cleaning these bathrooms, not complaining

00:12:23.100 --> 00:12:26.640
about my boss that's treating me like

00:12:24.899 --> 00:12:29.760
trash every single day, trying to get me

00:12:26.640 --> 00:12:31.620
fired, trying to conspire against me?"Because

00:12:29.760 --> 00:12:32.939
I could see in the spirit, I

00:12:31.620 --> 00:12:35.459
could warn of things that were going to

00:12:32.940 --> 00:12:37.680
happen. I would warn the pastor of the

00:12:35.459 --> 00:12:39.359
church about what was going on.

00:12:37.680 --> 00:12:41.819
So I started to develop a

00:12:39.360 --> 00:12:45.360
relationship with the pastor, and it

00:12:41.820 --> 00:12:47.519
took years of building.

00:12:45.360 --> 00:12:49.440
Then they came to

00:12:47.519 --> 00:12:51.480
me and said, "Hey, we know you can

00:12:49.440 --> 00:12:52.680
pray. People tell us all the time

00:12:51.480 --> 00:12:56.579
you're laying hands on people and they're

00:12:52.680 --> 00:13:00.599
