00:12:56.579 --> 00:13:02.880
building a reputation of, "Hey,

00:13:00.600 --> 00:13:04.980
if Brandon prays for you, the Lord's going to

00:13:02.880 --> 00:13:06.839
heal you."People on the staff

00:13:04.980 --> 00:13:08.880
started coming to me. "Hey, I've got a

00:13:06.839 --> 00:13:10.079
