00:13:17.880 --> 00:13:21.899
they would start singing, to be able to

00:13:20.459 --> 00:13:25.319
get through the service.

00:13:21.899 --> 00:13:27.420
It became a process. I'm the janitor that

00:13:25.320 --> 00:13:30.180
was cleaning and doing everything. Then

00:13:27.420 --> 00:13:32.339
people in witchcraft wanting to

00:13:30.180 --> 00:13:34.439
get free would come in there and get healed. None

00:13:32.339 --> 00:13:36.360
of them knew how to deliver anybody from

00:13:34.440 --> 00:13:39.000
a devil; they'd come and get me. I'm

00:13:36.360 --> 00:13:40.920
cleaning the toilets in church, or a

00:13:39.000 --> 00:13:42.360
vomit spill, or whatever from somebody

00:13:40.920 --> 00:13:44.579
