00:13:42.360 --> 00:13:46.860
"Hey, we gotta have you in the back in the altar

00:13:44.579 --> 00:13:48.899
room. A witch just gave her heart to

00:13:46.860 --> 00:13:50.040
Jesus Christ, and she's flipping out, and

