we don't know what to do with her

00:13:50.040 --> 00:13:53.639
because she's growling and manifesting

00:13:51.720 --> 00:13:55.500
back there. Can you come back here

00:13:53.639 --> 00:13:57.899
and cast the devil out of her because

00:13:55.500 --> 00:13:59.940
none of us know how to do it?"I said,

00:13:57.899 --> 00:14:01.440
"Are you kidding me? You are pastors."It

00:13:59.940 --> 00:14:02.760
was kind of an arrogance thing on my

00:14:01.440 --> 00:14:04.680
part because I was just like, "Whatever,

00:14:02.760 --> 00:14:06.899
you're coming to get me to do your job."But

00:14:04.680 --> 00:14:09.239
I just said, "Okay, fine."I had to be

00:14:06.899 --> 00:14:11.220
humble and just say, "Okay, I'll pray for her."So I'd

00:14:09.240 --> 00:14:13.440
go down there

00:14:11.220 --> 00:14:15.360
and start casting devils out of her. They'd

00:14:13.440 --> 00:14:17.399
come back there and say, "Listen, you're

00:14:15.360 --> 00:14:19.380
