00:14:19.380 --> 00:14:23.820
bit quieter because she's causing a

00:14:21.660 --> 00:14:26.279
distraction in church,

00:14:23.820 --> 00:14:28.860
and she's growling and everything."I

00:14:26.279 --> 00:14:29.639
said, "Listen, you deal with it

00:14:28.860 --> 00:14:32.220
then."Because

00:14:29.639 --> 00:14:35.639
I was already irritated about

00:14:32.220 --> 00:14:38.040
my circumstances. Lo and behold,

00:14:35.639 --> 00:14:40.079
this went clear on until about 11:30 at

00:14:38.040 --> 00:14:41.639
