00:14:40.079 --> 00:14:43.500
pastors came in there and said, "Can you

00:14:41.639 --> 00:14:44.940
tell the devils to hurry up

00:14:43.500 --> 00:14:46.440
and get out? Because I'm ready to go home

00:14:44.940 --> 00:14:48.720
and eat. I don't want to be here anymore."I

00:14:46.440 --> 00:14:51.120
said, "Go ahead and go home.

00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:53.040
I've got the alarm code and

00:14:51.120 --> 00:14:55.380
the key, don't worry about it. I'm going to

00:14:53.040 --> 00:14:57.000
get this girl set free."So lo and behold,

00:14:55.380 --> 00:14:58.980
they all left. You know, that's the way

00:14:57.000 --> 00:15:00.600
things went. I started getting a

00:14:58.980 --> 00:15:03.600
reputation. That's the way I live my

00:15:00.600 --> 00:15:05.820
faith. I believe God is a deliverer, I

00:15:03.600 --> 00:15:07.860
believe God is a healer, and regardless

00:15:05.820 --> 00:15:11.579
of my circumstances and what's going on

00:15:07.860 --> 00:15:13.680
