00:15:11.579 --> 00:15:15.479
let me start doing prayer.

00:15:13.680 --> 00:15:17.760
So, I started doing Saturday morning

00:15:15.480 --> 00:15:19.139
prayer whenever the main prayer lady was

00:15:17.760 --> 00:15:21.240
gone. When I led

00:15:19.139 --> 00:15:23.639
prayer, the presence of God

00:15:21.240 --> 00:15:25.199
would fill that whole atmosphere, and

00:15:23.639 --> 00:15:27.360
