00:15:25.199 --> 00:15:29.399
God would settle in so strongly. Whenever

00:15:27.360 --> 00:15:32.399
we would do prayer, it was nothing about

00:15:29.399 --> 00:15:34.860
me; it had everything to do with Jesus. I

00:15:32.399 --> 00:15:37.079
want to let you know, if God will use me,

00:15:34.860 --> 00:15:38.699
He will use you. I'm telling you, I'm

00:15:37.079 --> 00:15:40.199
nothing special. I'm just telling you about

00:15:38.699 --> 00:15:42.180
just being obedient to whatever the Lord

00:15:40.199 --> 00:15:44.060
told me to do. So, I just kept cleaning

00:15:42.180 --> 00:15:49.979
toilets. Ten

00:15:44.060 --> 00:15:51.479
years went by. On 3/3 of '13, the Lord

00:15:49.980 --> 00:15:54.720
says, 'You're done.'On 3/3 of '03,

00:15:51.480 --> 00:15:56.820
I was hired; on 3/3 of '13,

00:15:54.720 --> 00:15:57.660
He said, 'You're done. I want you to quit

00:15:56.820 --> 00:16:01.920
now.'I

00:15:57.660 --> 00:16:03.600
said, 'Are you serious? I

00:16:01.920 --> 00:16:07.040
don't mind being here anymore.'He said,

00:16:03.600 --> 00:16:07.040
'Yeah, I know. That's why you're released.'A

00:16:07.440 --> 00:16:12.959
