00:16:11.519 --> 00:16:14.899
stopped praying to be a part

00:16:12.959 --> 00:16:16.920
of doing that. He said, 'I'm going to

00:16:14.899 --> 00:16:19.019
do something different

00:16:16.920 --> 00:16:22.680
with your life now.'So, I

00:16:19.019 --> 00:16:25.800
stopped doing it.

00:16:22.680 --> 00:16:27.660
Six months goes by, and the pastor falls into

00:16:25.800 --> 00:16:29.099
an adulterous affair, and the church

00:16:27.660 --> 00:16:31.079
