00:16:29.100 --> 00:16:33.540
It was a very hard thing for me because

00:16:31.079 --> 00:16:35.699
I thought, 'Man, this is terrible.'I warned

00:16:33.540 --> 00:16:38.639
him about all the things that were

00:16:35.699 --> 00:16:41.099
coming prophetically. I warned him about

00:16:38.639 --> 00:16:43.320
all of it, and he still didn't listen. I

00:16:41.100 --> 00:16:45.240
spent years telling him,

00:16:43.320 --> 00:16:48.720
and you know what?

00:16:45.240 --> 00:16:50.820
I did my job. I did my job. I did it, and I

00:16:48.720 --> 00:16:52.980
honored him. I prayed for him, and I did

