00:17:25.859 --> 00:17:30.120
shelf. I started working and trying to

00:17:27.660 --> 00:17:32.160
make money. He would give me

00:17:30.120 --> 00:17:34.139
ideas. I would develop a

00:17:32.160 --> 00:17:35.700
