00:17:41.640 --> 00:17:44.880
Because it's just the way this little

00:17:42.780 --> 00:17:47.340
guy goes, 'Well, Jesus is sitting on my

00:17:44.880 --> 00:17:48.600
couch, I won't ask Him about scores and

00:17:47.340 --> 00:17:50.879
about the games. I'm going to talk to

00:17:48.600 --> 00:17:53.580
Jesus.'Whatever,

00:17:50.880 --> 00:17:55.440
dude. You don't have a clue; you have no

00:17:53.580 --> 00:17:58.020
relationship with Him at all. I'm going to

