and the doors are going to

00:22:17.460 --> 00:22:20.280
fling wide open for you for

00:22:19.140 --> 00:22:22.559
ministry now,

00:22:20.280 --> 00:22:24.360
because I have found that you fear

00:22:22.559 --> 00:22:26.639
Me, and you fear what I've asked you to

00:22:24.360 --> 00:22:27.959
do. You've been obedient.'And I said,

00:22:26.640 --> 00:22:29.700
'Lord, I don't want to do it.'Because, I

00:22:27.960 --> 00:22:31.320
said, 'My little girl is still overcoming.

00:22:29.700 --> 00:22:32.700
You want me to do a ministry? You want me to

00:22:31.320 --> 00:22:35.580
do all this stuff?'I said, 'I've run from it.'I

00:22:32.700 --> 00:22:37.620
actually was relieved that He had

00:22:35.580 --> 00:22:39.178
told me to do business. Because

00:22:37.620 --> 00:22:40.860
He had told me to

00:22:39.179 --> 00:22:42.780
invest in things, and it was being

00:22:40.860 --> 00:22:44.820
successful. The

00:22:42.780 --> 00:22:46.860
Lord started blessing my hands big time,

00:22:44.820 --> 00:22:48.960
and I was excited about it. And I said,

00:22:46.860 --> 00:22:51.959
'Man, for the first time we're actually able to pay our bills on time. For the first time we're

00:22:48.960 --> 00:22:54.360
able to

00:22:54.360 --> 00:22:59.699
not have to be on food stamps.'It

00:22:57.360 --> 00:23:01.799
was embarrassing not being

00:22:59.700 --> 00:23:03.539
able to pay your bills, to not be able to

00:23:01.799 --> 00:23:05.700
pay your electric or your water or your gas

00:23:03.539 --> 00:23:07.200
because you're so broke. And every single

00:23:05.700 --> 00:23:09.179
time you get to the end of the

00:23:07.200 --> 00:23:11.280
paycheck, you'd have to borrow on a

00:23:09.179 --> 00:23:13.140
credit card to get through because we were

00:23:11.280 --> 00:23:15.240
trying to pay for my daughter to go

00:23:13.140 --> 00:23:17.640
through therapy.

00:23:15.240 --> 00:23:20.700
We had nothing. We were broke,

00:23:17.640 --> 00:23:22.679
dead broke, working for the church. And

00:23:20.700 --> 00:23:24.720
like I said, we got

00:23:22.679 --> 00:23:26.580
out of the church, and my wife got out of

00:23:24.720 --> 00:23:28.500
college, and we thought, 'Man,

00:23:26.580 --> 00:23:30.899
we're going to be in the money now because

00:23:28.500 --> 00:23:33.120
she's got her master's

00:23:30.900 --> 00:23:34.559
degree.'Nope.

00:23:33.120 --> 00:23:36.000
Nothing happened with the master's

00:23:34.559 --> 00:23:39.600
degree. She still doesn't use her

00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:41.640
master's degree as of this moment.

00:23:39.600 --> 00:23:43.320
She is able to do taxes, she is

00:23:41.640 --> 00:23:45.960
able to do everything she needs

00:23:43.320 --> 00:23:47.760
to do; she has a lot of education.

00:23:45.960 --> 00:23:49.679
So,

00:23:47.760 --> 00:23:51.658
this is the process we've been in our

00:23:49.679 --> 00:23:54.659
life.

00:23:51.659 --> 00:23:56.700
I say all this to say, I hope that was

00:23:54.659 --> 00:23:57.900
not boring. I'm just trying to tell you

00:23:56.700 --> 00:24:01.200
where I come from.

00:23:57.900 --> 00:24:03.059
It has been a lot of trials. There has

00:24:01.200 --> 00:24:06.059
been a lot of 'I don't know if we're

00:24:03.059 --> 00:24:08.220
going to make it,'standing every single

00:24:06.059 --> 00:24:11.158
paycheck, standing and believing, cleaning

00:24:08.220 --> 00:24:13.799
the bathrooms, dying to self, the trials,

00:24:11.159 --> 00:24:15.600
and developing my

00:24:13.799 --> 00:24:17.340
relationship with Him to the point of

00:24:15.600 --> 00:24:18.899
thinking, 'Man, Lord, if You're ever going to

00:24:17.340 --> 00:24:20.158
use me.'And then He tells me, 'I'm not

00:24:18.900 --> 00:24:21.900
going to do that with you. I want you to

00:24:20.159 --> 00:24:24.179
do something else.'And for years I think

00:24:21.900 --> 00:24:25.620
the promise is gone. God doesn't want me to

00:24:24.179 --> 00:24:27.120
be a preacher. He doesn't want me

00:24:25.620 --> 00:24:28.760
to do anything like that. I'm

00:24:27.120 --> 00:24:33.959
going to be a businessman.

00:24:28.760 --> 00:24:36.000
And so, all that to say this: I'm here, and

00:24:33.960 --> 00:24:39.299
that's where I'm at right now. That

00:24:36.000 --> 00:24:41.100
is a lot of

00:24:39.299 --> 00:24:44.220
testimony of everything that I've been

00:24:41.100 --> 00:24:46.199
through up until today. And so, I'm here to

00:24:44.220 --> 00:24:47.520
tell you all about Jesus now on YouTube,

00:24:46.200 --> 00:24:50.159
because that's what He's told me to do,

00:24:47.520 --> 00:24:52.980
and I've been obedient to it. So, let me

00:24:50.159 --> 00:24:54.960
pray for you. If you have a dream, if you

00:24:52.980 --> 00:24:57.600
have

00:24:54.960 --> 00:24:59.100
some kind of call on your life, you feel

00:24:57.600 --> 00:25:00.539
God wants you to be in

00:24:59.100 --> 00:25:03.539
ministry, and you don't know how to get there,

00:25:00.539 --> 00:25:04.740
don't give up on it. You know what? I

00:25:03.539 --> 00:25:07.140
don't know where this is going to lead.

00:25:04.740 --> 00:25:09.179
I don't have any clue. All I know is

00:25:07.140 --> 00:25:11.100
God told me to be on YouTube, and you all

00:25:09.179 --> 00:25:12.900
are watching it. It's been very

00:25:11.100 --> 00:25:15.120
interesting for me because I now

00:25:12.900 --> 00:25:17.700
have 50,000 subscribers, and I started

00:25:15.120 --> 00:25:19.678
out, I believe it was

00:25:17.700 --> 00:25:21.780
February or whatever, doing these videos

00:25:19.679 --> 00:25:23.460
and putting ministry

00:25:21.780 --> 00:25:25.200
stuff on there, and people started

00:25:23.460 --> 00:25:26.820
subscribing. And He said, 'I'm going to breathe

00:25:25.200 --> 00:25:28.980
on it for you,'and that's exactly what

00:25:26.820 --> 00:25:31.200
He's done. So, I appreciate you all being

00:25:28.980 --> 00:25:32.760
a part of this. Like I said,

00:25:31.200 --> 00:25:34.980
I have no clue where it's going to go.

00:25:32.760 --> 00:25:36.779
All I know is I wake up every day

00:25:34.980 --> 00:25:39.360
still doing my business

00:25:36.779 --> 00:25:42.539
stuff, working, and doing this whenever I

00:25:39.360 --> 00:25:44.158
have time to. I just want to

00:25:42.539 --> 00:25:46.980
say thank you for helping and

00:25:44.159 --> 00:25:49.620
supporting me and being a part of it. Like

00:25:46.980 --> 00:25:51.360
I said, I believe God has put healing

00:25:49.620 --> 00:25:53.939
in my hands. I feel the fire in my hands

00:25:51.360 --> 00:25:56.219
when I pray for people. It's there for a

00:25:53.940 --> 00:25:58.679
reason. He told me one day I'll have

00:25:56.220 --> 00:26:00.720
a tent, and I'm going to go and set tents

00:25:58.679 --> 00:26:03.179
up. He wants me to have a

00:26:00.720 --> 00:26:05.760
tent revival. There's a great revival

00:26:03.179 --> 00:26:08.159
about to happen

00:26:05.760 --> 00:26:10.620
with tents and people being healed.

00:26:08.159 --> 00:26:12.600
I've seen it. Thank you for watching, and

00:26:10.620 --> 00:26:15.418
I pray you all have a wonderful day.

00:26:12.600 --> 00:26:18.418
Put a song in your heart and a smile on

00:26:15.419 --> 00:26:21.500
your face. Jesus loves you, and we'll see

00:26:18.419 --> 00:26:21.500
you next time. Bye-bye.

